dcterms:description: A Penn-style treebank that is lemmatised, part-of-speech tagged and annotated for constituent structure, with additional tagging for certain grammatical functions. It contains approximately 1,000,000 words from 61 text extracts spanning 10 centuries (1150-2008), covering all attested stages of Icelandic.
dcterms:title: Icelandic Parsed Historical Corpus (IcePaHC)
